Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.36,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the recovered Lan Fan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.57,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ed engages in combat with the Homunculus Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.58,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He works out a plan while his mettle is tested,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.45,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and successfully retrieves Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.25,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But Pride swallows Gluttony, a comrade of his,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and obtains his abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Elsewhere, Mustang has reunited with Hawkeye and his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:03.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They've kidnapped the Führer President's wife in order to hold her hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.48,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.32,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.57,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.07,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.36,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,This scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.70,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:28.50,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Hohenheim will have no choice but to show himself if I were to capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.27,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.70,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.04,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.66,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,it's Greed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.83,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,You scum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.46,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Give young master back his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.71,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.80,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:35.69,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm hasn't even fully recovered yet, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.49,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just worry about yourself for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need your help later, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.42,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.67,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I couldn't finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.88,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.38,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you for not being able to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.63,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Even from my perspective, he's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.77,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.94,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.61,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in Kanama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Since when...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now! Pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:41.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, the Homunculus Pride is inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.55,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard everything from Mr. Gorrilius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.63,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,It's Darius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Drats...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It felt so disgusting. It was as if he was interfering with my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.90,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,They're like the alter ego of my alter ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.82,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're my son, it's probably easier for them to interfere with your soul through the blood seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.00,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Please treat his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.50,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,How are things going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.38,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Edward's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.97,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,The shadowy monster devoured Gluttony, and we hardly stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.81,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Greed and Edward are fighting him, but things aren't looking too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in danger because I was captured by Pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:45.69,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,There's an unlimited source of light due to the fire, and I've already used up all of my flash bangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.57,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use that same trick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.20,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.62,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the people living in the slums will be dragged into it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're a skilled alchemist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.80,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask of you, considering your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.89,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.23,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,The view is pretty clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.99,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,No use in taking cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.95,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape from my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.99,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.83,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,More or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.33,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be worrying about others right now, Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.92,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much more you can take at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.42,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:50.18,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,A rather rude way to address your sibling, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.43,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I eat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:56.18,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Eat me and you'll have a stomachache, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.73,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Finally decided to show yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.61,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:10.15,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are supposed to show up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.82,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.78,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,So you think you're able to defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.20,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.21,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty scary, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.09,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,What is he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.89,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Is he aiming for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:50.99,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:59.45,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a disappointing strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.29,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't know when to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.68,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,So he came back, just to be taken hostage again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.19,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is quite the odd one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.32,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.48,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,...to make fun of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.17,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.98,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.52,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He actually sealed him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You got Al stuck in there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.67,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.17,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It was Al's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use your ability in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.39,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really a cause for celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.43,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.85,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,If you crack open an exit to leave even for an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.31,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll use my shadow and-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the slightest intention of getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we engage in a test of wills, Selim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No, Homunculus Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:00.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,My body doesn't require oxygen, light, or even food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to quietly sit here with me for the entire day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,until the Promised Day comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.71,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating Pride in his current state would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:16.92,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And if we were to let him run loose,\Nit would cause massive damage to the surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.72,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Al offered to use himself as a decoy to trap him without engaging in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.93,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we've gained some time to work out a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys didn't even discuss it with me-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.56,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.86,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,"If I were to tell Brother, he'd definitely be against it."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:40.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He did the best he could to think of a way that would keep everyone alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.62,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start with putting this fire out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for doing this just after we were reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But I had to, because I was the one who caused this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:14.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I only have to be in here for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.78,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Lust is gone, Envy is gone, and Gluttony now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.54,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath is at the the joint exercise in the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.46,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,and Pride can't move right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:38.25,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones left at Central right now are Father and Sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.51,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed! What the hell are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Told you earlier, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.72,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the king of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:12:00.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think there's been a lot of Ishbalans in Central lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.15,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.12,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's a group of them near the abandoned building to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.95,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Ishbalans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.95,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the lad with the cross-shaped scar who used to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.04,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, speak of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.25,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,We were just talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.51,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a slum by the name of Kanama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kanama is located on the edge of town,\Nin the forest to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.35,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.60,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, isn't the little girl with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:38.11,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one who was\Ncarrying around a black and white cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.11,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,She actually came back here a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.99,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.49,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't go back to her country?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.41,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,What is she up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.37,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were the ones behind it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who blew up Bradley in his train in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.00,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Blew up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.80,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,This is news to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:07.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I figured you teamed up\Nwith the other Ishbalans and did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:12.47,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone was saying that\Nthey were going to commit terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't gather here to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:21.77,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,They're good friends of ours who seek to change this country in a method other than terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.63,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I should stop being so enthusiastic about my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.01,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I've soiled my new suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:54.43,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The real performance starts after daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:09.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way my dad would make it so easy for a child to be able to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:19.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when you make fun of humans so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:23.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't know anything about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't think that everything will go your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Same with that scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.64,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,From my perspective, it's just careless planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.76,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You call us human sacrifices,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:42.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems as though you're planning on using us to accomplish something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What if we were to escape outside the country for the fear of our own safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, your plan would have been completely ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:58.25,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, there are humans who believe that their safety comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.29,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.92,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for example, Wrath's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:09.47,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,There once was a time when I was about to be hit by a car in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:15.76,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to save me, ready to sacrifice her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.44,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Though she doesn't know I'm a homunculus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.86,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely taken aback by her desperate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:33.62,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had a father, but never a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:37.12,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, to be honest, her existence was fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.33,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I began to wonder whether that's what having a mother was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath's wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Bradley, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.50,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how low you are to deceive such a kind soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.89,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It {\i1}was{\i0\fscx40} {\r} as if we were playing a game of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.93,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fun living with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.48,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,and I do love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.27,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,There are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:16.91,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,There are humans, like Wrath's wife, who would throw away their own life to protect something dear to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.37,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,And those of you who were chosen to be human sacrifices,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.58,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,possess a strong heart, even out of those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.13,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd throw away this country and flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.80,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, you came back here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.26,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a hint of carelessness in our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.49,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.70,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.66,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.85,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,What in the name of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.40,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.48,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this mound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.11,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't Jerso and Zampano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:37.99,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Darius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:44.37,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me Kimblee sent you here to eliminate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.12,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.58,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, high?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.33,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped working for Kimblee months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:52.67,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that to get us off guard, and then you're planning to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.76,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.80,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.51,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Heinkel's probably hiding somewhere over there, ready to ambush us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.85,Default-alt,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being so insistent, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Marcoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.97,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.10,Default-alt,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fight, Porky Pig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.10,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.27,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,That's Zampano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:04.97,Default-alt,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,You-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So Scar was with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:05.98,Default-alt,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.94,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,The gorilla said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to rush you when you just arrived, but we should make arrangements asap-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't pigs, fatties and gorillas learn to get along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.82,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Are you picking a fight, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:24.95,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you guys really did stop working for Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:30.29,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,If we kept working for him, he'd just dispose of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.83,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.51,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Well thanks to that, we're fugitives now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.05,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,but it does feel nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.22,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:39.97,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.68,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,those guys definitely won't abandon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.27,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,It'll finally begin once the sun comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.19,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.40,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll all live to see the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.03,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they've come to terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.41,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the old man run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He went to go scout out the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.83,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:11.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He said that it would end up being more convenient,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,since he's the only one whose face hasn't been seen by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:23.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd go and check up on a couple of things, such as Colonel Mustang's movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but for the most part, I think he's worried about the whereabouts of Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.14,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.02,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done making arrangements with Scar and them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:34.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The plan has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.19,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.49,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,So it's time at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.08,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother is pretty gutsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.13,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,He's trapped in there with that monster in pitch darkness, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.59,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I would have gone crazy by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al's giving it his all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Promised Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:28.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.09,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Denny! Denny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.59,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Denny!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:07.97,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.39,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.68,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You need to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.60,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Or else it'll begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.27,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,What'll begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.56,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,The solar eclipse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:19.02,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Solar eclipse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:23.61,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... what time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.69,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too early for the solar eclipse to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.74,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Don't look at the sun with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:30.03,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.37,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:35.91,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.50,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,There's smoke rising from town!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.76,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave the house today, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:59.23,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Cedi Squad in the western district reporting.\NWe've discovered Mustang and his men in District C75.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.60,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.48,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,However, they have the Führer President's wife as hostage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.73,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,and it's very difficult for us to attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:08.74,Default,Clem,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:09.61,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.58,Default,Clem,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Roy Mustang stays alive, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:17.50,Default,Clem,0000,0000,0000,,The woman means nothing to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:21.33,Default,Clem,0000,0000,0000,,Have her killed along with Mustang's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.15,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot everyone except for Colonel Mustang!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:03.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The peace-accustomed masses are oblivious to the crisis right before their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:07.80,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They can't even begin to imagine the destruction awaiting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:13.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:17.10,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 50, Upheaval in Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:22.52,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The weak reel in loss, and the strong trample them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:25.02,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
